The,GSMA,is,an,association,of,mobile,operators,worldwide,Representing,more,than,mobile,operators,in,more,than,countries,the,GSMA,supports,the,standardizing,deployment,and,promotion,of,the,GSM,mobile,telephone,system,The,GSMA,also,produces,industry,leading,events,such,as,the,Mobile,World,Congress,and,Mobile,Asia,Expo,The,GSMA,OneAPI,is,a,set,of,APIs,that,expose,network,capabilities,over,HTTP,The,OneAPI,Payment,interface,allows,users,to,charge,mobile,subscribers,for,use,of,their,Web,application,or,content,The,API,supports,direct,charging,of,users,as,well,as,reserving,funds,from,a,user,s,account,for,subsequent,charging,It,uses,both,REST,and,SOAP,protocols,with,responses,in,XML,and,JSON